99-0602 (La. 4/1/99)

STATE of Louisiana v. James E. DIVERS. No. 99-KK-0602. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Divers, James E; — Defendants); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs; Parish of Ouachita 4th Judicial District Court Div. “F” Number 46,968; to the Court of Appeal, Second Circuit, Number 32296-KW

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J. and JOHNSON, J. would grant the writ. KIMBALL, J. not on panel.
